title: RB Alvin Ross rushes for 374 yards in team's win
text: RB Alvin Ross rushes for 374 yards in team's win Ed O'Brien PaPreps.com Publisher This season has seen a lot of running backs have phenomenal performances. Greensburg Central Catholic running back Alvin Ross is the latest to join that group based on his performance against Serra Catholic in Week 5.The 5-foot-10, 160 pound, junior running back, rushed for 374 yards on 26 carries and scored four touchdowns in the win for his team. Ross scored on runs of 55, 67, 70, and another 70 yards in GCC's 42-10 win over Serra Catholic.Check out video from his performance below:
